snippet.title: Watch Dogs 2 - Gameplay Walkthrough - E3 2016
snippet.description:
Visit Watch Dogs at http://www.watchdogs.com

Watch the first-ever WATCH_DOGS 2 gameplay walkthrough, in which Marcus and his Dedsec allies infiltrate the home of a social media mogul. In this mission, Dedsec is looking to expose the CEO of popular social media platform, !NViTE, who is using the citizens’ personal data to engineer a corrupt voting process.
